<item>
            <title>[CXF-4742] Not possible to disable token renewal in STS client</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CXF-4742</link>
                <project id="12310511" key="CXF">CXF</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;There&apos;re properties in org.apache.cxf.ws.security.trust.STSClient:&lt;br/&gt;
sendRenewing, allowRenewing&lt;br/&gt;
Unfortunately they don&apos;t prevent the renewal from being issued.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;p.s. We have a real usecase where thirdparty use STS service but don&apos;t support the renewal&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Affected version: 2.7.1&lt;/p&gt;</description>
